title: Decide: Succeed or Die Trying
itunes:title: Decide: Succeed or Die Trying
description:
Episode 162 - Do you really want to succeed? Then you must get rid of your back up plan! If you know what you want to do and you know it's your passion then there is no reason to have a Plan B because all it does is distract you from Plan A. In this episode I dive deeply into this topic and how to make your Plan A your only plan.
